1
00:00:04,550 --> 00:00:08,430
Your eyes really are a beautiful color.
Do you have contacts?

2
00:00:08,430 --> 00:00:09,800
Yeah, I guess so.

3
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:12,390
Then wear them starting tomorrow.

4
00:00:12,390 --> 00:00:13,260
Okay.

5
00:00:14,510 --> 00:00:16,560
So, what did you mean by "the first time"?

6
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:20,230
Doing someone's makeup.
Seeing how happy it makes them.

7
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:22,730
It makes me happy too.

8
00:00:22,730 --> 00:00:25,440
You'll look even better with contacts.

9
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:26,780
I can't wait.

10
00:00:26,780 --> 00:00:28,320
(He looks so happy...)

11
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:30,320
(He really does love makeup...)

12
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:36,580
(I guess I really
can't do my own makeup.)

13
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:39,210
(That kind of magic... I hope I can do that someday...)

14
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:50,510
Alright, class is starting.

15
00:00:50,510 --> 00:00:51,970
Sorry, I'm sitting over there today.

16
00:00:51,970 --> 00:00:54,680
Huh? What?

17
00:00:58,180 --> 00:00:59,640
Huh?

18
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:02,060
The contacts look good.

19
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:05,110
You're the one who told me to wear them.

20
00:01:05,110 --> 00:01:08,690
Alright, so for today,
we're going to be working on group presentations.

21
00:01:08,690 --> 00:01:11,280
Please get into groups with the people around you.

22
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:14,200
Makoto, let's team up.

23
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:17,370
I don't mind, but what about them?

24
00:01:17,370 --> 00:01:19,330
Eh, don't worry about them.

25
00:01:19,330 --> 00:01:22,500
It's an odd number anyway.
If I stay there, someone will be left out.

26
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:26,000
Alright~

27
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,630
One representative from each group
will come up to present.

28
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:30,880
About the presentation...

29
00:01:32,050 --> 00:01:33,380
Makoto, you wanna present?

30
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:35,350
I'll leave it to you, Yuki.

31
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,810
Fair enough.

32
00:01:38,010 --> 00:01:38,970
Yuki?

33
00:01:38,970 --> 00:01:39,930
Hm?

34
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:41,770
Your hand...

35
00:01:42,890 --> 00:01:44,480
Oh...
